title: GoAtma - Sword In The Darkness
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

There is no better way to end successful and highly productive year for Neogoa Records than with the new discovery of our latest artist coming from Israel, GoAtma. Sword In The Darkness is perfect representation of his addiction to Goa trance vibes and, as alluded to in his name (“Atma” is a Hindi word for spirit), it is very spirited and cheerful music. Download Sword In The Darkness - http://www.neogoa.net/sword-in-the-darkness

Tracklist:

01 - Sword In The Darkness (148 BPM) 
02 - Cosmic Consciousness (148 BPM) 
03 - Spiritual Chanting (148 BPM) 
04 - Shabatayom (150 BPM)

For more free Goa trance and ambient music, please visit us:
